{"tid":404173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家咁討厭同埋仇視公廁？其實佢哋先係Girlfriend material!","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T21:29:03.000Z","uid":147022,"like":26,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7562831e2ccbf3187383965b31c353afbe35a2","tid":404173,"uid":147022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"其實搵公廁做女朋友真係一流！以我所認識嘅公廁通常都好nice，好識待人接物，好好相處，你有乜嘢困難都好肯幫你。而且一般女仔能夠成為公廁，都係因為佢地嘅外表係有返咁上下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/073401_fd0dd03c9b100dd48a7a16de3bce6ecf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F073401_fd0dd03c9b100dd48a7a16de3bce6ecf.jpg&h=00e8abc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲女仔選擇做公廁其實都係為咗有更強大嘅connection，女仔後生識咁諗其實真係好唔錯。各行各業嘅人你女朋友都一定會識啲，無論係做生意/搵工佢一定會幫到你。有一個公廁做你女朋友，世界嘅脈絡將會被掌控於你手中！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/073808_74588f38a727639c432ba981ab819b20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F073808_74588f38a727639c432ba981ab819b20.jpg&h=483bf157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女仔願意做公廁代表佢哋對sex嘅接受嘅程度好大，一般女仔咁玩嘅，佢哋玩得更厲害；普通女仔唔敢玩嘅，佢哋都敢玩。一般香港女仔最多咪同你玩震蛋；佢哋唔同，SM、野外露出、fisting、屎眼哩啲少不免，你有冇諗過你可以同自己女朋友玩4p? 仲要另外兩條女係佢幫你搵埋？你諗唔諗到睇住自己d兄弟上自己條女係有幾咁興奮？結咗婚之後玩埋換妻你都咪話唔過癮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/074112_0b4c6fe1d152a21e9bdfb6a5e7243772.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F074112_0b4c6fe1d152a21e9bdfb6a5e7243772.jpg&h=20039be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人會話，有好多公廁都可能落過仔，點接受到呀？凶宅喎，好唔老黎架喎。Come on James~ 而家咩年代呀，生過仔嘅女人嘅身體先係最吸引人，因為佢哋嘅身體先至算係完全成熟。佢哋粒lin又黑又大粒真係睇到都覺得興奮，每邊用個有鈴鐺嘅乳夾夾住黎屌，一路推車一路聽住有節奏嘅ling ling 聲，嗰種感覺真係只應天上有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/073145_b2ddff8eec0e90fd2fa6f2bf4f9b335b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F073145_b2ddff8eec0e90fd2fa6f2bf4f9b335b.jpg&h=4514967f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有如果你搵個未大過肚嘅女人，你屌到佢大肚之後如果佢個身體變到你唔鍾意咁嘅樣，你到時先退貨就麻撚煩啦。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/074316_177aff5ef6f17c22cf340f4daf0c00d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F074316_177aff5ef6f17c22cf340f4daf0c00d3.jpg&h=aa08ab5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Conclusion: 識搵女朋友嘅一定要搵公廁！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6b6aa264fe3afa28fde9779dc82642b275ab3b","tid":404173,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主咁博愛"},{"pid":"dac30c3f1aed6647bbb4e4fb50cd9245484b1470","tid":404173,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:49:47.000Z","msg":"樓主識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41063b23eaf37f1dfdf9925110324acc20c721d8","tid":404173,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:50:24.000Z","msg":"公廁都吹奏"},{"pid":"f8fc43f00cf7555218d41a47990c6f4c8b0caf68","tid":404173,"uid":115445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"LM 撐巴打"},{"pid":"667c9dc6101c24695cec953b6713c01636ac9786","tid":404173,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬威武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d8618017a360e5c13061afbc6c212bae25520d","tid":404173,"uid":4